creator: 株式会社ワークス
descriptionHtml:
"Do you eat rice or bread for breakfast?"
To put an end to this conversation, the battle between Rice and Bread has begun!!

Play with Rice and Bread in 5 kinds of minigames in each mode.
You can get items with different ranks depending on your score in each game.
Equip Rice or Bread with the items you've collected, and it's time for a showdown!!
The outcome will be decided by which items you've equipped, in an exciting ending!
Which will be chosen for breakfast?!

Enjoy the breakfast illustrations seen at the end
and have fun collecting your own original Rice and Bread pictures with their equipped items.

There's also a Challenge Mode that only those who've cleared up to the ending can play!
descriptionShort: Which will be chosen for breakfast?!
